name: Filling void, Head#14, 2020
description:
watercolors, acrylic, digital print on old paper, coffee and collage hannemuhle paper, cm 20x30
part of the series Filling Void, a collection of mixed media works started mid 2020 trying to investigate the opposite concepts of full and void with painting, collage and digital print, in this case the silhouette of a bust portrait mixed with old images and discarded pieces of painting.
